{"tid":1465971,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"西九李錦聯 Ben哥廚房","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T19:19:01.000Z","uid":119330,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"37f2031f40ed33f16d27dc76e745f70b8037a877","tid":1465971,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:27:08.000Z","msg":"前排睇報導 知道李錦聯入左西九開舖<br />\n想試下公仔箱大廚係咪咁堅料<br />\n早幾日入左去試伏<br />\n<br />\n選擇黎講 唔算多 都係雞牛豬果D<br />\n今次試既 就係宣稱用走地雞 醃一晚 慢煮一個鐘 吹乾幾個鐘既雞飯<br />\n<br />\n老實講 係好食既 雞無乜脂肪 肉唔&quot;鞋&quot; 算嫩滑<br />\n雞味算係濃<br />\n但唔好期望真係會食到&quot;嘩&quot;一聲<br />\n<br />\n雞飯黎講 真係令我食到&quot;嘩&quot;一聲<br />\n得黃竹坑熟食市場早幾年前海南雞飯先有咁高質<br />\n<br />\n味道上黎講 算係偏淡<br />\n同食白切雞差不多 略帶咸味 但就稍為偏乾 無咁油 <br />\n雞皮 幾爽滑<br />\n<br />\n跟雞上 唔係傳統薑蒜 黑豉油 果類醬汁<br />\n而係一兜雞湯 算係有少少特別<br />\n<br />\n飯 普通白飯 無乜特別<br />\n<br />\n整體上評價 無伏 食得過<br />\n<br />\n不過 雞飯黎講 都係鍾意肥少少<br />\nD脂肪好似啫喱咁 係皮同肉之間"},{"pid":"2743f6a26cc674ee552af1de85d793d8332b6866","tid":1465971,"uid":222646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:28:08.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"e8b59564fa7cc60446bdae95ec5b5b9be35e77c8","tid":1465971,"uid":119330,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"2743f6a26cc674ee552af1de85d793d8332b6866","tid":1465971,"uid":222646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:28:08.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:39:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vcg4Muq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvcg4Muq.jpg&h=81d9dc26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已補"},{"pid":"2ded72f9d32909a978a6b7333e43f5f2010f8c9e","tid":1465971,"uid":97071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:09:58.000Z","msg":"幾銀"},{"pid":"9cfa2536cf36175482bd9d5da5dc4c0831b3e395","tid":1465971,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:43:21.000Z","msg":"樣好似ok"},{"pid":"a7ee3c0caf03d014418c8757e3f4d0de694fe901","tid":1465971,